NOTE: BusinessWeek Online (http://www.businessweek.com) and LeadersOnline
(http://www.leadersonline.com), the Web unit of executive recruiter
Heidrick and Struggles, have published the premiere issue of
LeadersOnline, the companion magazine to their joint Web site
(www.businessweek.com/careers/). The October/November issue
provides original career information and commentary, plus content
from BusinessWeek Online. The joint BusinessWeek Online-LeadersOnline
Web site provides a meeting place for middle and upper managers worldwide.

The LeadersOnline cover story looks at how an executive recruiter
might go about choosing the next President. Other features:
Co-CEOs: Does it Work?; Ready to Switch Career Gears and Become a
"Techie"?, and a retrospective from flex-time pioneers.
For more information about the BusinessWeek Online/LeadersOnline
magazine or Web site contact Andrew Palladino: 212 512-2680.



